  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_08_su_0003"> 
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_deep_green" lang="y">곱의 소수점 위치가 달라지는 규칙을 알아봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>
        
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y"><span class="small_bg_sky">가</span>에서 찾을 수 있는 규칙을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="wrap"> 
            <div class="note-paper f24b">
              <div class="paper-con">
                <p lang="y">가</p>
                <span>0.15×1 &equals; 0.15</span>
                <span>0.15×10 &equals; 1.5</span>
                <span>0.15×100 &equals; 15</span>
                <span>0.15×1000 &equals; 150</span>
              </div>
              <div class="paper-con">
                <p lang="y">나</p>
                <span>150×1 &equals; 150</span>
                <span>150×0.1 &equals; 15</span>
                <span>150×0.01 &equals; 1.5</span>
                <span>150×0.001 &equals; 0.15</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center justify_center dir_row f32b gap_10">
              <span lang="y">곱하는 수가 10 배, 100 배, 1000 배가 될수록 곱의 소수점이</span>
              <div class="dropdown_wrap answer1"> 
                <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="오른쪽으로">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value="왼쪽으로"></option>
                  <option value="오른쪽으로"></option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <span lang="y">한 자리씩 옮겨집니다.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y"><span class="small_bg_sky">나</span>에서 찾을 수 있는 규칙을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="wrap"> 
            <div class="note-paper f24b">
              <div class="paper-con">
                <p lang="y">가</p>
                <span>0.15×1 &equals; 0.15</span>
                <span>0.15×10 &equals; 1.5</span>
                <span>0.15×100 &equals; 15</span>
                <span>0.15×1000 &equals; 150</span>
              </div>
              <div class="paper-con">
                <p lang="y">나</p>
                <span>150×1 &equals; 150</span>
                <span>150×0.1 &equals; 15</span>
                <span>150×0.01 &equals; 1.5</span>
                <span>150×0.001 &equals; 0.15</span>
