            </div>
            <div class="flex align_center justify_center dir_row f32b gap_10">
              <span class="flex align_center gap_10" lang="y">
                <span>곱하는 수가 </span>
                <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span>
                <span>배,</span>
                <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>100</span></span>
                <span>배,</span>
                <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>1000</span></span>
